15,01I am sane
15,01I am real
15,01I know I think
15,01I see I feel.

15,01The world is cold
15,01Our lives are sad
15,01I break its bonds
15,01It thinks me mad.

15,01I know my mind
15,01I know it works
15,01But yet behold
15,01How I am cursed.

15,01Because I'm sane
15,01I am judged mad
15,01Prounced so by
15,01The hatter band.

15,01The inmates judge
15,01The wardens claim
15,01The verdict summed:
15,01A life of pain.
